      • plot

        public static void plot(DataSet dataSet)
        Plot a data set. This method will produce a scatter plot of the data values against the integers from 0 to n - 1, where n is the size of the data set.
        Parameters:
        dataSet - the data set to plot.

      • plot

        public static void plot(DataSet firstDataSet,
                        DataSet secondDataSet)
        Plot the first data set against the second data set. The first data set will be plotted on the x-axis, while the second data set will be plotted on the y-axis.
        Parameters:
        firstDataSet - the data set to plot on the x-axis.
        secondDataSet - the data set to plot against the first data set.
